&gt; Hi Cecelia,
&gt;
&gt; Does ESMF provide support routines for halo communication for unstructured meshes \(using the mesh class obviously\)? I can't seem to find any information on this. I can see that redist is supported for coupling between components but I see nothing on halo updates for infra component communication.
&gt;
&gt; I guess I should check that I should be using the mesh class for a cubed sphere grid - am I doing the right thing?
&gt;
&gt; Your documentation also states that you don't currently support a hexagonal mesh \(well it actually says what you do support but pentagons and hexagons are missing\) - is that right? If so, are there any plans to add support for these in the future?
